The paper deals with generative modeling of 3D shapes, which is a problem relevant to Computer Vision (cs.CV), Graphics (cs.GR), and Virtual Reality (cs.MM). The use of Variational AutoEncoders (VAEs) also suggests a connection to Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
